title: Apply to Your Gorgeous, 2 Bedroom Senior Apartment TODAY!
posting_body: ['Let us introduce you to an apartment that will exceed your expectations!', 'The Cambric Senior Apartments, in Dayton’s Bluff, offers both 1 and 2 bedroom floorplans.', 'These spacious apartments have other convenient amenities as well, including a fully equipped beauty salon, heated underground parking, a community room, and even an in-home washer and dryer.', 'Reserve your luxurious apartment today!', 'Please call for pricing and details.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Just Steps Away From Mississippi Market', '- Gorgeous Landscaped Property & Well-Kept Community Spaces', '- Private Patio or Balcony Space (select homes)', '- Separate Dining & Living Room Areas', '- Open & Spacious Floor Plans', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Cambric Apartments is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income limits & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,3800.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Cambric Apartments', '720 East 7th Street', 'St. Paul, MN, 55106', '<URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.']
